<div id="review_1511897070" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1511897070" />
    <a title="Barbara Guner" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/51514020-barbara-guner"><img alt="Barbara Guner" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1511897070?book_show_action=true">Jan 16, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Barbara Guner" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Barbara Guner" href="/user/show/51514020-barbara-guner">Barbara Guner</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780749399214" href="/book/show/2036481.An_Instant_In_The_Wind">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1511897070" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3386979439516034407">Set in the 18th Century in South Africa, a white woman finds herself alone in the desert with a runaway slave. After a rather dry beginning, the book literally warms up to become absolutely amazing. The descriptions are brilliant and moving - the relationship between the woman and the slave is heartrending. It is based on true facts. Definitely a book to read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

