<span id="freeTextContainer11553972499206273423">Beautifully written, Brink&apos;s account of the relationship between a white woman and black slave as they try to get back to civilization across the harsh, unfriendly wilds of South Africa. Set in the 18th century, this book explores so many different themes : love, self-discovery, survival, politics. Wonderful descriptions of the landscape. </span>
