<div id="review_1036024184" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1036024184" />
    <a title="Melissa Hinde" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/27187266-melissa-hinde"><img alt="Melissa Hinde" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1408968483p2/27187266.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1036024184?book_show_action=true">Aug 25, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Melissa Hinde" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Melissa Hinde" href="/user/show/27187266-melissa-hinde">Melissa Hinde</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140080148" href="/book/show/734812.An_Instant_in_the_Wind">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1036024184" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer925073806503944442">I first read this book about 25 years ago and was absolutely swept away by it. On one level the outcome is predictable but it is nevertheless utterly compelling and spellbinding. I love Andre Brink&apos;s novels and for me this is his masterpiece.</span>
  <span id="freeText925073806503944442" style="display:none">I first read this book about 25 years ago and was absolutely swept away by it. On one level the outcome is predictable but it is nevertheless utterly compelling and spellbinding. I love Andre Brink's novels and for me this is his masterpiece.</span>
  <a data-text-id="925073806503944442" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


