    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1942846110" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8330457921939381496">Exquisitely well written, Undeniably magical. <br/><br/>André Brink bring us to South Africa colonial period for telling a superb romantic and intense story with unforgettable characters. The details abour narrative is surprising. <br/><br/>Definitely, An Instant in the Wind is an Instant Classic.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


